_sText:
zm_murendz

Few notes about this map:

This is a small map.
Has no secret.
Has 1 place that is hard to find.
Has lighting.
Works.
Has several places to be in.

Credits:
Niiskunkoppa
Emnu

Installation:
1. Extract murendz.rar to desktop
2. Copy the maps folder in the .rar file to 
steam\steamapps\USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\
3. Then play the game.

Installation troubleshooting for newbies:

Q: How can i extract the murends.rar file?
A: Press it with mouse2 and choose extract to folder murendz

Q: When i press the .rar file with mouse2, i cant see the extract option
A: Download WinRAR
